tags.name: Rosenwald School Historical Marker
tags.note: A historic marking near the intersection of School Street and George Mason Blvd. tells about the history of the school site. The entire parcel on both sides of George Mason Blvd. are being developed by Madison Homes as "Eleven Oaks".
